_sText: MINIGAME_SMOKEWARS_UNREAL 4 Fragxl.com community with love MAP FEATURES: [+] FragXL.com stuff [+] 2 Extra HP [+] Smoke recharger [+] Anti-smoke [+] "Smooth curvez" [+] Music [+] Limited time [+] More, more & more...
